Name: Riqui Puig
Number: 5
Position: Midfielder
Goals: 1
Assists: 3

Riqui Puig is a creative midfielder with a great vision of the game and great skill.
Riqui Puig started at Barça in the Under-16 category, coming from Jàbac Terrassa. 
At La Masia he improved as a player and has grown steadily through the categories. 
He made his debut with Barça B against the Gimnàstic Tarragona in the 2017/18 season. 
His performance with the reserves marveled the fans and he became the undisputed star 
of that game. For the 2018/19 season, he is playing for Barça B.
